<section class="pt-24 pb-20 bg-bg" id="about" aria-labelledby="about-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-center max-[768px]:grid-cols-1 max-[768px]:gap-12">
      <div class="font-display text-[clamp(1.75rem,3vw,2.5rem)] font-normal italic leading-[1.3] text-text relative pl-7 before:content-[''] before:absolute before:left-0 before:top-1.5 before:bottom-1.5 before:w-1 before:bg-accent before:rounded [&_strong]:font-semibold [&_strong]:not-italic [&_strong]:text-primary reveal">
        „Exzellente Therapie entsteht nur dort, wo sich <strong>Therapeuten wohlfühlen</strong> – und Patienten sich <strong>verstanden fühlen</strong>."
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-5">
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-1">
          <span class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase text-primary">Über die Praxis</span>
