          <p class="text-[1.0625rem] text-text-muted leading-[1.7] max-w-150">
            Unter der Leitung der staatlich geprüften Logopädin <strong>Emel Şimşek-Uçar</strong> bietet unsere moderne Praxis fundierte Diagnostik, Beratung und Therapie für Menschen aller Altersgruppen – von der frühen Kindheit bis ins Seniorenalter.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 mt-2 reveal reveal-delay-2">
          <div class="bg-surface border border-border rounded-md p-5 shadow-sm">
            <div class="font-display text-[2rem] font-bold text-primary leading-none mb-1">100%</div>
            <div class="text-[.8125rem] text-text-muted font-medium">Zweisprachige Versorgung DE &amp; TR</div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-surface border border-border rounded-md p-5 shadow-sm">
            <div class="font-display text-[2rem] font-bold text-primary leading-none mb-1">4</div>
            <div class="text-[.8125rem] text-text-muted font-medium">Therapiebereiche für alle Altersgruppen</div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-surface border border-border rounded-md p-5 shadow-sm">
            <div class="font-display text-[2rem] font-bold text-primary leading-none mb-1">2 min</div>
            <div class="text-[.8125rem] text-text-muted font-medium">vom Duisburger Hauptbahnhof</div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-surface border border-border rounded-md p-5 shadow-sm">
            <div class="font-display text-[2rem] font-bold text-primary leading-none mb-1">3. OG</div>
            <div class="text-[.8125rem] text-text-muted font-medium">Barrierefrei per Aufzug erreichbar</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="block w-full overflow-hidden leading-0 [&_svg]:block [&_svg]:w-full mt-16" aria-hidden="true">
